                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18401019-2596-offence-1 t18401019-cd-183"></join>9th of October</rs>, 36 pairs of gloves, value 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 16<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. the goods of <persName id="t18401019-name-969" type="victimName">
